Big Sur Valley



Looking out towards Andrew Molera State Park, at the mouth of the Big Sur River,
from the "Valley View" loop of the Pfeiffer Falls trail.
Taken Monday, June 25, 2001, 10:41:11am.  Original image size: 1600x1200, 1011kb
